frontmatter.title: Emphasize values
frontmatter.description: Personal values matter, especially during challenging times. Find ways to emphasize values within the given structure and confines.

frontmatter.title: Demonstrate what's important
frontmatter.description: It's easy to get caught up in the details and be sidetracked by others. Make it easier with a better structure to each day that emphasizes importance in the right places.

frontmatter.title: Actions demonstrate values
frontmatter.description: Others can only judge by what is observable. What you put out creates the image that others see.
